{"schemaVersion":1,"bookId":"toefl-sentences","unitId":"sentence-006","title":"Sentence 06","sectionId":"sentences-001","sectionTitle":"Sentence 01-10","pageStart":49,"pageEnd":54,"extractionMethod":"text-layer","wordEntryCount":39,"duplicateEntryCount":0,"pages":[{"number":49,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Sentence 06"},{"type":"text","text":"Perfectly matched pearls, strung into a necklace, bring a far higher"},{"type":"text","text":"price than the same pearls sold individually."},{"type":"text","text":"完美搭配的珍珠串成一条项链，能带来比单颗售卖高得多的价"},{"type":"text","text":"钱。"},{"type":"section","text":"语法笔记"},{"type":"text","text":"本句的主干是Perfectly matched pearls bring a far higher price。过去"},{"type":"text","text":"分词matched表被动，作前置定语修饰pearls；strung into a necklace是过"},{"type":"text","text":"去分词短语作后置定语；a far higher price than是比较结构，比较的对象"},{"type":"text","text":"是“perfectly matched pearls, strung into a necklace”和the same pearls sold"},{"type":"text","text":"individually。"},{"type":"section","text":"核心词表"},{"type":"entry","text":"perfectly /ˈpɜːrfɪktli/ ad. 完美地；完全地","headword":"perfectly"},{"type":"note","text":"同义 faultlessly ad. 完美地"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 perfect a. 完美的 vt. 使完美"},{"type":"text","text":"perfection n. 完美"},{"type":"entry","text":"string /strɪŋ/ vt. 悬挂；系；串在一起","headword":"string"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 细绳；一串；弦"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 string sth. out 使分开成一列；拖延…的时间"},{"type":"note","text":"同义 thread n. 细绳；线 vt. 穿过；穿成串"}]},{"number":50,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"individually /ˌɪndɪˈvɪdʒuəli/ ad. 单独地；个别地","headword":"individually"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 in（不）+di（二）+vid（分开）+ually→不能一分为二的→"},{"type":"text","text":"单独地"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 individual a. 单独的；个别的 n. 个人"},{"type":"text","text":"individuality n. 个性"},{"type":"text","text":"individualism n. 个人主义"},{"type":"text","text":"individualize vt. 使个性化"},{"type":"section","text":"主题归纳"},{"type":"text","text":"与“首饰”相关的词："},{"type":"entry","text":"accessory /əkˈsesəri/ n. 装饰品；配饰","head